{"id":208424,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/02/global-voices-希腊：“我签备忘录之前没先看过”/","date":"2012-02-05T07:19:54Z","modified":"2012-02-05T07:19:54Z","title":"Global Voices | 希腊：“我签备忘录之前没先看过”","content":"<p><p>2012 年一月廿三日希腊前劳工与社会安全部（2010）及经济竞争与运输部（2009）部长 Louka Katseli 透漏她只有三小时阅读国际货币基金组织关于希腊信贷危机对策的<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2010–2011_Greek_protests\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2010%E2%80%932011_Greek_protests\">备忘录</a>，震惊全国人民。</p>\n<p>现任发展竞争与运输部长、前任国民保护部长 Michalis Chrysochoidis 在<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.dailymotion.com/video/xnyo7l\" href=\"http://www.dailymotion.com/video/xnyo7l\">晨间电视访问</a>中承认他在签署国际货币基金组织备忘录之前并没有先读过其内容，他辩解说自己“当时有其他对抗犯罪的任务在身。”：</p>\n<p> </p>\n</p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/14334763@N05/3257259155\"><img title=\"Minister Manolis Chrysochoidis. Photo by Flickr user Piazza del Popolo (CC BY 2.0).\" src=\"http://farm4.staticflickr.com/3402/3257259155_6822218a67_m.jpg\" alt=\"Minister Manolis Chrysochoidis. Photo by Flickr user Piazza del Popolo (CC BY 2.0).\" width=\"240\" height=\"180\" /></a></p>\n<p>Manolis Chrysochoidis 部长。照片来自 Flickr 用户 Piazza del Popolo (CC BY 2.0)。</p>\n</div>\n<p>消息在網絡上迅速传开，部份网友对此反应极负面，也出现了一些贬损的侮辱性言词，表现出大家对政治系统的唾弃，以及对部长藉口的嘲笑。</p>\n<p>在一两个小时内这个事件的标签 <a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/search?q=%23De_diavasa_to_mnimonio_giati\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/search?q=%23De_diavasa_to_mnimonio_giati\">#de_diavasa_to_mnimonio_giati</a>（我没有读备忘录，因为……）已经在推特上成为全球性的<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://twitpic.com/8b30h3\" href=\"http://twitpic.com/8b30h3\">热门话题</a>：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/northaura/status/161742551576096768\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/northaura/status/161742551576096768\">@northaura</a>：整个推特因为 Crysochoidis 部长“我没读备忘录”的发言变得热闹滚滚，标签是 <a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/search?q=%23De_diavasa_to_mnimonio_giati\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/search?q=%23De_diavasa_to_mnimonio_giati\">#De_diavasa_to_mnimonio_giati</a>。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>全球之声作者兼编辑 Asteris Masouras (<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/asteris\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/asteris\">@asteris</a>) 收集了各式文章、照片和推特。底下是一部份希腊网友的推特留言和意见：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/agamemnon_st/status/161879484075749377\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/agamemnon_st/status/161879484075749377\">@agamemnon_st</a>：既然研究备忘录和法律不是你的工作，为什么你是国会议员？</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://www.facebook.com/news247/posts/304769946235843\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/news247/posts/304769946235843\">George Kallis</a>：太无耻了，你该在自己脖子上套个枷锁！！你的签名毁了希腊。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://twitpic.com/8bi31i\"><img title=\"'The Dark Knight returns to fight crime on Athens' mean streets'. Image mocking Minister Chrysochoidis' statement. Photo via Twitpic by @Teacherdude.\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/dark-knight-272x300.jpg\" alt=\"'The Dark Knight returns to fight crime on Athens' mean streets'. Image mocking Minister Chrysochoidis' statement. Photo via Twitpic by @Teacherdude.\" width=\"272\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<p>“黑暗骑士归来，雅典街头打击犯罪”。嘲弄 Chrysochoidis 部长的图片。来自推特 @Teacherdude。</p>\n</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/ngeor/status/161734941237985280\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/ngeor/status/161734941237985280\">@ngeor</a>：<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/search?q=%23De_diavasa_to_mnimonio_giati\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/search?q=%23De_diavasa_to_mnimonio_giati\">#De_diavasa_to_mnimonio_giati</a> 我是被选来领导大家，而不是来读备忘录的。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/Ovelikios/status/161726536431575040\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/Ovelikios/status/161726536431575040\">@Ovelikios</a>：我没读过备忘录，不过我看了电影版。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/natachef/status/161730754114629632\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/natachef/status/161730754114629632\">@natachef</a>：<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/search?q=%23De_diavasa_to_mnimonio_giati\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/search?q=%23De_diavasa_to_mnimonio_giati\">#de_diavasa_to_mnimonio_giati</a> 我没读备忘录，因为电邮附件打不开。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/Stathisgr/status/161729716242497537\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/Stathisgr/status/161729716242497537\">@Stathisgr</a>：Mnimonio？Lol，正忙着殴打示威群众。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/mpampakis/status/161720868026843136\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/mpampakis/status/161720868026843136\">@mpampaki</a>：我得对抗犯罪。罗宾发烧了，小丑又绑架了高登警长的儿子。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/nchrysoloras/status/161761060330815488\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/nchrysoloras/status/161761060330815488\">@nchrysoloras</a>：<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/search?q=%23De_diavasa_to_mnimonio_giati\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/search?q=%23De_diavasa_to_mnimonio_giati\">#de_diavasa_to_mnimonio_giati</a> 我没读备忘录，因为只有<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chuck_Norris_facts\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chuck_Norris_facts\">查克．罗礼士</a>读了。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/mirsiniloizou/status/161760655362371587\"><img title=\"Twitter user @mirsiniloizou posted: \"and here, the photo of #didn't_read_memorandum_because\". Photo shows \"protagonists of the day\" Ms. Katseli and Mr. Chrysochoidis.\" src=\"https://p.twimg.com/Aj6wdYHCMAARP8U.jpg\" alt=\"Twitter user @mirsiniloizou posted: \"and here, the photo of #didn't_read_memorandum_because\". Photo shows \"protagonists of the day\" Ms. Katseli and Mr. Chrysochoidis.\" width=\"215\" height=\"182\" /></a></p>\n<p>推特用户 @mirsiniloizou：“这是 #didn&#39;t_read_memorandum_because 代表照片。”，照片中是“本日最佳领导者”Katseli 女士和 Chrysochoidis 先生。</p>\n</div>\n<p>在受到强烈批评后 Chrysochoidis 在脸书状态上<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://www.facebook.com/chrisochoidis/posts/10150536152082954\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/chrisochoidis/posts/10150536152082954\">更新</a>：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>我想澄清并确认我的重点。是的，我再说一遍，我没有读过备忘录。我没有处理里面的文字、程序或“该有的”谈判。我可没有以此为 傲。我也不是为了逃避责任才这样说的，正好相反，我认为这是我政治生涯中最大的错误之一。我在关键时刻专注在小事 —— 我身为部长的责任上，而不是更重要的身为国家领导人之一所该负的责任上。我说这些是因为大家都必须改变。我们习惯相信每个领导人、每个总理，国会的投票、 同意政府的决定。这种模式已然不再。现在需要的是集体和个人负起责任和贡献己力。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>去年政府和国会议员因为接受国际货币基金组织备忘录以及对社会经济危机毫无作为而受到严厉批评，使其中一些人出来捍卫自己的信念和政治行动。</p>\n<p>2011 年十月前 PASOK 国会议员 Thomas Rompopoulos 发表了另一项“免责声明”，他在广播节目中<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HcZnyK2GdBA\" href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HcZnyK2GdBA\">说</a>：“没人有时间读这备忘录，我没读，其他人也没读。我们授权经济部长 Papakonstantinou 去签署。这是信任问题。”：</p>\n</p>\n<p>除了 Chrysochoidis 部长受到的强烈指责之外，许多网友也不光是在社群媒体上批评政治情势，同时也怪自己“盲目”纵容政客的恶劣行为：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=1726015587\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=1726015587\">Panagiotis Giannoudis</a>：希腊国会万岁！</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/helena_chari/status/161723300857397248\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/helena_chari/status/161723300857397248\">@helena_chari</a>：希腊不需要大规模毁灭性武器，有政客就够了！</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.skai.gr/news/politics/article/192569/m-hrusohoidis-den-diavasa-to-mnimonio/\" href=\"http://www.skai.gr/news/politics/article/192569/m-hrusohoidis-den-diavasa-to-mnimonio/\">dangler69</a>：所以到底有没有人读过备忘录？也许那些被赶出国会的？</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/Dr_Troy/status/161747460232974336\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/Dr_Troy/status/161747460232974336\">@Dr_Troy</a>：<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/search?q=%23De_diavasa_to_mnimonio_giati\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/search?q=%23De_diavasa_to_mnimonio_giati\">#De_diavasa_to_mnimonio_giati</a> 我没读备忘录，因为即使大家现在嘲笑我，到时候还是会投我一票。群众是善忘的……#bitter_truth</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/cpil/status/161745307481292800\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/cpil/status/161745307481292800\">@cpil</a>：你自己又读了吗？</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/MilitaryRaiden/status/161712771585679360\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/MilitaryRaiden/status/161712771585679360\">@MilitaryRaiden</a>：大家都对 Chrysochoidis 对自己无能的自白感到惊讶，却不觉得投票给他的笨蛋们还有投票权这件事也令人惊讶吗。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/tgeorgakopoulos/status/161754515220074496\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/tgeorgakopoulos/status/161754515220074496\">@tgeorgakopoulos</a>：嘘，听！安静，听的到吗？是国会议员办公室里两百九十九台印表机的声音，他们正在列印备忘录。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/sVathis/status/161722462571200512\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/sVathis/status/161722462571200512\">@sVathis</a>：希腊人从不看说明书的。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>隔天，Arkoudos 苦涩的总结希腊经济和社会危机最悲哀的一面：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/arkoudos/status/162083527637221376\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/arkoudos/status/162083527637221376\">@arkoudos</a>：我不是付了 DEI（希腊公营能源企业）的特别税了吗？噢，真抱歉，没去读，我忙着卑躬屈膝找工作，晚餐才有饭吃。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div>校对：<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"使用者:Portnoy\" href=\"http://proj.daodin.net/mediawiki/index.php/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%80E5%B8%8C%E8%85%8A%EF%BC%9A%E2%80%9C%E6%88%91%E7%AD%BE%E5%A4%87%E5%BF%98%E5%BD%95%E4%B9%8B%E5%89%8D%E6%B2%A1%E5%85%88%E7%9C%8B%E8%BF%87%E2%80%9D&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F02%2F04%2F10354%2F&#038;description=&#038;via=sticker\" title=\"HEMiDEMi\"><span>HEMiDEMi</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://myshare.url.com.tw/index.php?func=newurl&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F02%2F04%2F10354%2F&#038;desc=%E5%B8%8C%E8%85%8A%EF%BC%9A%E2%80%9C%E6%88%91%E7%AD%BE%E5%A4%87%E5%BF%98%E5%BD%95%E4%B9%8B%E5%89%8D%E6%B2%A1%E5%85%88%E7%9C%8B%E8%BF%87%E2%80%9D\" title=\"MyShare\"><span>MyShare</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.shouker.com/%22%20onclick=20js=document.createElement%20(\" title=\"Shouker\"><span>Shouker</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F02%2F04%2F10354%2F\" title=\"facebook\"><span>facebook</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F02%2F04%2F10354%2F&#038;text=%E5%B8%8C%E8%85%8A%EF%BC%9A%E2%80%9C%E6%88%91%E7%AD%BE%E5%A4%87%E5%BF%98%E5%BD%95%E4%B9%8B%E5%89%8D%E6%B2%A1%E5%85%88%E7%9C%8B%E8%BF%87%E2%80%9D&#038;via=globalvoiceszh\" title=\"twitter\"><span>twitter</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://reddit.com/submit?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F02%2F04%2F10354%2F&#038;title=%E5%B8%8C%E8%85%8A%EF%BC%9A%E2%80%9C%E6%88%91%E7%AD%BE%E5%A4%87%E5%BF%98%E5%BD%95%E4%B9%8B%E5%89%8D%E6%B2%A1%E5%85%88%E7%9C%8B%E8%BF%87%E2%80%9D\" title=\"reddit\"><span>reddit</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.stumbleupon.com/submit?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F02%2F04%2F10354%2F&#038;title=%E5%B8%8C%E8%85%8A%EF%BC%9A%E2%80%9C%E6%88%91%E7%AD%BE%E5%A4%87%E5%BF%98%E5%BD%95%E4%B9%8B%E5%89%8D%E6%B2%A1%E5%85%88%E7%9C%8B%E8%BF%87%E2%80%9D\" title=\"StumbleUpon\"><span>StumbleUpon</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://del.icio.us/post?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F02%2F04%2F10354%2F&#038;title=%E5%B8%8C%E8%85%8A%EF%BC%9A%E2%80%9C%E6%88%91%E7%AD%BE%E5%A4%87%E5%BF%98%E5%BD%95%E4%B9%8B%E5%89%8D%E6%B2%A1%E5%85%88%E7%9C%8B%E8%BF%87%E2%80%9D\" title=\"delicious\"><span>delicious</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.instapaper.com/edit?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F02%2F04%2F10354%2F&#038;title=%E5%B8%8C%E8%85%8A%EF%BC%9A%E2%80%9C%E6%88%91%E7%AD%BE%E5%A4%87%E5%BF%98%E5%BD%95%E4%B9%8B%E5%89%8D%E6%B2%A1%E5%85%88%E7%9C%8B%E8%BF%87%E2%80%9D\" title=\"Instapaper\"><span>Instapaper</span></a></span></p>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=738338\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"738338\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheet/embeddedform?formkey=dGRpN3FrVThuMFFsZHBZcmNGLW94dEE6MQ\" width=\"450\" height=\"309\" frameborder=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\">Loading&#8230;</iframe></p>\n","author":1001,"categories":[20534],"tags":[3764,19748]}